<section class="main" id='ride'>
  <article>
    <div class="entry-content">
      <div class="container-fluid ride-top-wrapper">
        <div class="container page-container px-0">
          <div class="page-heading-cont py-4 py-lg-5">
            <h2 class="page-top-heading"><span><span class="mr-1" style="font-size:40px; font-weight:200;">THE</span> <span class="ml-2" style="letter-spacing:15px;"> RIDE<span></span></span></span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 px-0 d-flex flex-wrap">
              <div class="col-12 col-md-4 p-2">
                <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                  <div class="premium-banner">
                    <div class="premium-banner-inner">
                      <!--                      <img width="1500" height="1400" src="images/card_image_07.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="" loading="lazy">-->
                      <%= image_tag 'ride/card_image_07.jpg', alt: 'HIGH/RIDE', width: "1500", height: "1400", class: "attachment-full size-full"%>
                      <div class="premium-banner-inner-desc">
                        <div class="premium-banner-desc-centered">
                          <div class="premium-banner-title-wrap"><h3 class="premium-banner-ib-title mb-4">SPOKEHAUS 45</h3></div>
                          <div class="premium-banner-ib-content mb-5">
                            <p>Kick–ass, high intensity, low impact full body workout on a bike — our signature ride.
                              <br>
                              <br>
                            </p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-4 p-2">
                <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                  <div class="premium-banner">
                    <div class="premium-banner-inner">
                      <!--                      <img width="1500" height="1400" src="images/card_image_08.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="" loading="lazy">-->
                      <%= image_tag 'ride/card_image_08.jpg', alt: 'HIGH/RIDE', width: "1500", height: "1400", class: "attachment-full size-full"%>
                      <div class="premium-banner-inner-desc">
                        <div class="premium-banner-desc-centered">
                          <div class="premium-banner-title-wrap"><h3 class="premium-banner-ib-title mb-4">HIGH / RIDE</h3></div>
                          <div class="premium-banner-ib-content">
                            <p>Our version of a rave on a bike. Two instructors, one kick-ass ride (for intermediate to advanced riders).</p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-4 p-2">
                <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                  <div class="premium-banner">
                    <div class="premium-banner-inner">
                      <!--                      <img width="1500" height="1400" src="images/card_image_09.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="" loading="lazy">-->
                      <%= image_tag 'ride/card_image_09.jpg', alt: 'HIGH/RIDE', width: "1500", height: "1400", class: "attachment-full size-full"%>
                      <div class="premium-banner-inner-desc">
                        <div class="premium-banner-desc-centered">
                          <div class="premium-banner-title-wrap"><h3 class="premium-banner-ib-title mb-4">HOTBOX</h3></div>
                          <div class="premium-banner-ib-content">
                            <p>Ride with us in a 80° – 84° room, same class… but you will experience a greater level of detoxification, increased calorie burn and improved athletic performance in 45 minutes.</p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container-fluid expect-section py-3">
        <div class="container px-0 py-1">
          <div class="col-12 expect-wrapper p-2">
            <div class="heading-cont pt-1 pb-3">
              <h2 class="expect-heading mb-3 text-uppercase text-center">what  to expect</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 expect-boxes-cont d-flex flex-wrap pt-3 mt-2 px-0">
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 expect-box">
                <div class="box-head pb-1">
                  <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">FIRST RIDE</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="box-content">
                  Getting started is easy — arrive early (we recommend 15 minutes before) and our concierge will sign you in, get you to sign a waiver and set you up safely and properly on the bike.<br>
                  Once set-up and given a brief tutorial by our team on the hand and height positions — clip in and listen to your body, if something feels off — the team is available at any time to help.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 expect-box">
                <div class="box-head pb-1">
                  <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">Shoes</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="box-content">
                  Spin shoes are required to ride. We offer them complimentary at check-in or if you have your own, feel free to bring them in. Our pedals are<span> <b> SPD compatible.</b></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 expect-box">
                <div class="box-head pb-1">
                  <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">Water</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="box-content">
                  Hydration is super important, before, during and after a SPOKEHAÜS class — we offer filtered water bottle filling stations in the studio — as well as bottled water available for $2 at check-in.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 expect-box">
                <div class="box-head pb-1">
                  <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">Don't be late</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="box-content">
                  At SPOKEHAÜS we close our studio doors 1 minute before class start time. Unfortunately, if you are late for class we will not be able to let you in past the scheduled start time of class — it is quite disruptive to the other riders. We will be more than happy to reschedule you for another ride.
                  Once set-up and given a brief tutorial by our team on the hand and height positions — clip in and listen to your body, if something feels off — the team is available at any time to help.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 expect-box">
                <div class="box-head pb-1">
                  <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">Amenities</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="box-content">
                  We offer a fully stocked men’s and women’s change-room equipped with showers. We think you will love getting ready with us after your ride. Enjoy MALIN+GOETZ apothecary products in our washrooms, hair dryers, hair straighteners, curling irons, hairspray, razors, deodorant… the list goes on and on. If you need it, we have it.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 expect-box">
                <div class="box-head pb-1">
                  <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">Getting There</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="box-content">
                  <span><b>PARKING</b> </span>— Street parking is available on Dan Leckie Way as well as Fort York Blvd. for $2.25/hour.<br>
                  <span><b>PUBLIC TRANSIT</b></span> — Take the 511 Bathurst Streetcar to Fort York, walk east to Dan Leckie Way, South on Dan Leckie will take you straight to the HAÜS on your right.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 expect-box">
                <div class="box-head pb-1">
                  <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">CANCELLATION POLICY</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="box-content">
                  Can't ride? Please cancel your booking 6 hours before your ride time. If cancelled 6 hours prior to class time, your ride credit will be immediately refunded to your account. If cancelled within the 6 hour late cancellation window, you will lose your credit.
                  Once set-up and given a brief tutorial by our team on the hand and height positions — clip in and listen to your body, if something feels off — the team is available at any time to help.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container-fluid booking-section">
        <div class="container px-0 pb-3">
          <div class="booking-heading-cont px-2 pt-5 pb-2">
            <h2 class="booking-heading mb-0 text-uppercase text-center">How to Book</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 px-0 d-flex flex-wrap book-steps-cont">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4 step-box text-center p-2">
              <div class="box-img-cont pb-2">
                <%= image_tag 'ride/11.png', alt: 'HIGH/RIDE', width: "108", class: "attachment-full size-full mb-3"%>
              </div>
              <div class="box-head pb-1">
                <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">Pick your class + bike</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="box-content">
                Choose when you’d like to come in and which bike you’d like to ride.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4 step-box text-center p-2">
              <div class="box-img-cont pb-2">
                <%= image_tag 'ride/no2.png', alt: 'HIGH/RIDE', width: "108", class: "attachment-full size-full mb-3"%>
              </div>
              <div class="box-head pb-1">
                <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">Buy Credits</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="box-content">
                Each credit corresponds to a class.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4 step-box text-center p-2">
              <div class="box-img-cont pb-2">
                <%= image_tag 'ride/no3.png', alt: 'HIGH/RIDE', width: "108", class: "attachment-full size-full mb-3"%>
              </div>
              <div class="box-head pb-1">
                <h2 class="box-title mb-3 text-uppercase">Register</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="box-content">
                So we can book your class and save any credits you’ve purchased.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid booking-sect">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="col-12 p-2 text-center">
          <div class="py-3">
            <h2 class="book-heading"><%= link_to 'Book A Class', calendar_path, class: "book-a-class" %> <i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i></h2>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
